0871A46B.Toast: Help Timue check on other infected.

1EADAE68.Callback2Header: Get Timue's gifts for the infected

259D49BB.Phase15Description: I found Baridan and delivered Timue's package. He told me that Duraya can usually be found deeper in the Marsh.

2642177F.Phase37Description: The bandits were kidnapping the infected and harvesting their growths to sell to alchemists. I destroyed their operation and should bring the news to Timue.

3226125E.Phase54Description: I found Duraya and delivered Timue's package. She told me that Baridan usually stays close to Timue's house.

9367FF5C.Phase34Description: Raldin was looking for his brother when he was ambushed by the bandits. He overheard them talking of a camp where they were taking infected. I should go there and put a stop to the kidnappings.

A5EFB09D.Phase26Description: I saved Raldin from a group of bandits who were trying to take him. I should talk to him about it.

D53BFF05.Phase0Description: One of Timue's duties is to tend to the other infected that wander the swamp, but she is unable to do so this time. She wants me to take food and medicine to several infected in her stead.

E2223B19.Phase22Description: I've found Baridan and Duraya and delivered Timue's packages to them. The third, Raldin, was last seen in the north-east area of the swamp near the border with the snakemen.
